ot; height=&quot;22&quot;&gt;Quản trị thanh menu (tr&amp;ecirc;n, dưới, tr&amp;aacute;i)&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 16.5pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl67&quot; style=&quot;height: 16.5pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot; height=&quot;22&quot;&gt;Quản trị file upload&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;agrave;i thuyết tr&amp;igrave;nh Slide tr&amp;igrave;nh b&amp;agrave;y &amp;yacute; tưởng thiết kế trang web. &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;N&amp;ecirc;u ra điểm mới, s&amp;aacute;ng tạo, giải quyết vấn đề m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c trang web kh&amp;aacute;c đang gặp phải&amp;hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;3. Quy định t&amp;aacute;c phẩm dự thi&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Website chứa th&amp;ocirc;ng tin đầy đủ về lĩnh vực được chọn.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- C&amp;aacute;c lĩnh vực/chủ đề phải ph&amp;ugrave; hợp với thuần phong, mỹ tục Việt Nam kh&amp;ocirc;ng li&amp;ecirc;n quan đến ch&amp;iacute;nh trị, t&amp;ocirc;n gi&amp;aacute;o, &amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Sử dụng ng&amp;ocirc;n ngữ Tiếng Việt hoặc Tiếng Anh&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Giao diện website phải l&amp;agrave; duy nhất, kh&amp;ocirc;ng vi phạm bản quyền v&amp;agrave; được thiết kế sau khi cuộc thi được ph&amp;aacute;t động, nếu BGK t&amp;igrave;m thấy giao diện website của đội n&amp;agrave;o đ&amp;atilde; tồn tại trước khi cuộc thi ch&amp;iacute;nh thức bắt đầu th&amp;igrave; đội dự thi sẽ bị loại.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;4. Ti&amp;ecirc;u ch&amp;iacute; cuộc thi&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- &amp;Yacute; tưởng: &amp;Yacute; tưởng, s&amp;aacute;ng tạo, độc đ&amp;aacute;o v&amp;agrave; duy nhất.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Bố cục: Bộ website c&amp;oacute; tối thiểu c&amp;aacute;c chức năng đề ra trong bảng chức năng ch&amp;iacute;nh của website &amp;ldquo;t&amp;ugrave;y thuộc v&amp;agrave;o lĩnh vực của trang web&amp;rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Thẩm mỹ: Đảm bảo t&amp;iacute;nh mỹ thuật.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Kỹ thuật: Ứng dụng tốt c&amp;aacute;c kiến thức về HTML, CSS, Javascript, bootstrap, jquery &amp;hellip;.,&amp;nbsp; hiển thị tốt tr&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c tr&amp;igrave;nh duyệt.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;5. C&amp;Aacute;C V&amp;Ograve;NG DỰ THI&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Đăng k&amp;yacute;:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;24/05/2020 &amp;ndash; 30/05/2020&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tất cả c&amp;aacute;c đội dự thi c&amp;oacute; thời gian từ ng&amp;agrave;y 22/05/2020 đến 31/05/2020 để đăng k&amp;yacute; tham gia cuộc thi.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- V&amp;ograve;ng loại:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;01/06/2020 - 05/07/2020&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- C&amp;aacute;c đội tham gia sẽ trải qua 2 v&amp;ograve;ng loại:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;+ V&amp;ograve;ng sơ loại: (01/06/2020 &amp;ndash; 07/06/2020) C&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;oacute;m sẽ tr&amp;igrave;nh b&amp;agrave;y &amp;yacute; tưởng thiết kế website, l&amp;yacute; do, mục ti&amp;ecirc;u, c&amp;aacute;ch giải quyết vấn đề th&amp;ocirc;ng qua sản phẩm website.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;+ V&amp;ograve;ng loại: (01/07/2020 &amp;ndash; 05/07/2020) Ban gi&amp;aacute;m khảo sẽ đ&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; lựa chọn c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;oacute;m xuất sắc để lọt v&amp;agrave;o v&amp;ograve;ng chung kết.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- V&amp;ograve;ng chung kết:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;25/07/2020 &amp;ndash; 31/07/2020&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;h3&gt;1. Participants:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;a) All students currently studying at the School of Information and Communication Technology, Vietnam - Korea University of Information and Communication Technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;b) Each group has a minimum of 2 members and a maximum of 3 members&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://sict.udn.vn/uploads/2020/05/23/banner-bwd-2020.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;2. Content:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;a) Designing website interface on registered topics.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;b) Project to be submitted must include:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Static Web with technology of HTML, CSS, CSS3, Javascript, bootstrap, jquery ...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Video introduction to promote the Website (For final round)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Products must achieve at least the basic functions of the Website by 2 areas:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;table class=&quot;tai_lieu&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;colgroup&gt;&lt;col style=&quot;width: 48pt;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; /&gt;&lt;col style=&quot;mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 14921; width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot; /&gt;&lt;/colgroup&gt;\r\n&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes; mso-yfti-irow: 0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl63&quot; style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; width: 48pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; height=&quot;23&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl64&quot; style=&quot;width: 306pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MAIN FUNCTIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 33.75pt; mso-yfti-irow: 1;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl65&quot; style=&quot;height: 33.75pt; width: 48pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; height=&quot;45&quot;&gt;1.&lt;span class=&quot;font6&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl66&quot; style=&quot;width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot;&gt;Interface (brand identity system, characteristics of field of activity, arts, colors)&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; mso-yfti-irow: 2;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl65&quot; style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; width: 48pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; height=&quot;23&quot;&gt;2.&lt;span class=&quot;font6&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl66&quot; style=&quot;width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot;&gt;Home page&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; mso-yfti-irow: 3;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl65&quot; style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; width: 48pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; height=&quot;23&quot;&gt;3.&lt;span class=&quot;font6&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl66&quot; style=&quot;width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot;&gt;Module Introduction&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; mso-yfti-irow: 4;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl65&quot; style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; width: 48pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; height=&quot;23&quot;&gt;4.&lt;span class=&quot;font6&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl66&quot; style=&quot;width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot;&gt;Product / Service Module&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; mso-yfti-irow: 5;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl65&quot; style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; width: 48pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; height=&quot;23&quot;&gt;5.&lt;span class=&quot;font6&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl66&quot; style=&quot;width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot;&gt;Product management module&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; mso-yfti-irow: 6;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl65&quot; style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; width: 48pt; text-align: center;&quot; width=&quot;64&quot; height=&quot;23&quot;&gt;6.&lt;span class=&quot;font6&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;td class=&quot;xl66&quot; style=&quot;width: 306pt;&quot; width=&quot;408&quot;&gt;Price list&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 17.25pt; mso-yfti-ir